0700 2009</em></p>'),(3749,'2010-05-02 15:27:07',219,150,'<p>These cards show who is getting email about changes to cards in each of these sets:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{+*right+by name}}</p>'),(3752,'2010-05-02 15:28:16',219,150,'<p>These cards show who is getting email about changes to cards in each of these sets ([[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/Notification|learn more about notification]]):</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{+*right+by name}}</p>'),(3753,'2010-05-02 15:28:41',219,150,'<p>These cards show who is getting email about changes to these cards ([[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/Notification|learn more about notification]]):</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{+*right+by name}}</p>'),(3754,'2010-05-02 15:29:04',219,150,'<p>These cards show who is getting email about changes to these cards or card types. ([[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/Notification|Learn more about notification.]]):</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{+*right+by name}}</p>'),(3755,'2010-05-02 15:32:08',73,150,'<h1>Basics <em></em></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>Site name:</em> {{*title|closed;type:Phrase}}</p>\n<p><em>Home card:</em> {{*home|closed;type:Phrase}}</p>\n<p>{{*logo|closed;type:Image}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Sets / Settings</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Wagn allows you to apply <em>settings</em> (configuration options) to <em>sets </em>(groups) of cards.&nbsp; A set may be as general as all cards...</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*all|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>..or as specific as a single card, or somewhere in between.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{settings|open}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Accounts<br></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>Settings for inviting people, requesting accounts, and getting  accounts approved  ([[http://wagn.org/wagn/account#Administering%20accounts|learn more  about accounts]]). See below to set the address that account-related  emails come from, or to create a form for people who sign up.<br></em></p>\n<p>{{*invite|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*request|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*signup|closed}}<