ote>'),(6490,'2013-05-24 22:27:20',80,149,'<p>{{Cards|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{{Types|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{{Rules|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>'),(6491,'2013-05-24 22:28:12',152,149,'<p><em><span>Cards and [[images]] in this Wagn are copied to new Wagns</span></em>. Exceptions should be added here:</p>\n<p>{{*ignore|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This one updates automatically:</p>\n<p>{{cards to copy to new Wagns|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>What comprises those cards</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>this is way out of date - see [[default cards]], from wagn.org so needs some tweaking</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{Set+*type|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Settings+*type|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{list of rules|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{Cardtype+*type|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{cardtype descriptions|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{Role+*type|closed}}</p>\n<p>[[*account]], [[WagnBot]], [[Anonymous]]</p>\n<p>[[*to]], [[*from]], [[*thanks]], [[Invite Success]], [[Signup  Success]], [[Request Sent]]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[Config]]</p>\n<p>{{Config+*inclusions|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*sidebar+*inclusions|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Related tab</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[*account+*right+*content]] - available on any card that has the account extension</p>\n<p>Available on every card, because they\'re in [[*related]]:</p>\n<p>{{Related subtabs - universal|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Cards useful for Wagneering</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[by name+*right+*content]]</p>\n<p>[[by update+*right+*content]]</p>\n<p>[[by create+*right+*content]]</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Process</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Everything about default Wagns that can be done within cards (except permissions, see below) happens here. Make changes that make sense to you, and watch what each other are doing on Recent. There\'s space for discussion at the bottom of this page if you like.</li>\n<li>To <strong>migrate</strong> cards you add or change here to existing Wagns, put  a note in the [[http://wagn.org/Next_Wagn_Release|next Wagn release\'s]]  discussion about which cards you want migrated.</li>\n<li>Cards that are <strong> deleted</strong> should also be noted as migrations if it would cause a problem to leave them in. Otherwise, add them to the list at  http://www.wagn.org/wagn/migrations+to_delete (we only migrate deletions once in a  while).</li>\n<li>Default [[http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions|<strong>permissions</strong> are  specified on wagn.org]], because we want people to be able to choose among several different initial setups.</li>\n<li><strong>Document</strong> changes and additions at http://wagn.org/Default_cards and http://wagn.org/star_cards</li>\n<li>Things you remove from [[Config]] that may be relevant later can be added to http://www.wagn.org/wagn/en+not_ready</li>\n<li>Anything that involves code should be [[http://wagn.org/new/Ticket|ticketed]] on wagn.org</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Todo</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Content / Wagneering<br></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Adapt or include [[default cards]] for the \"What comprises...\" section above.</li>\n<li>Test and tweak http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions (ongoing)</li>\n<li>make *ignore a Search that returns Users, Account Requests, and things referred to by *ignore+tag. (Requires changing the dump a little, but could bring new users in with less overhead.)&nbsp; <em>eventually.&nbsp;&nbsp; not ready for this yet --efm</em></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Documentation<br></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>When documenting tickets that relate to [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Installation+tickets_for_item|installation]] or [[http://wagn.org/wagn/administration+tickets_for_item|administration]], make sure to update [[Config]]. (make search to show ones from current/recent releases?)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Discussion</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(6492,'2013-05-24 22:28:12',154,149,'[[Ethan McCutchen]]\r\n[[John Abbe]]\r\n[[Lewis Hoffman]]\r\n[[*ignore]]\r\n[[cards to copy to new Wagns]]\r\n[[new]]\r\n[[all non-star cards]]\r\n[[cards by type]]\r\n[[Cardtype descriptions]]\r\n[[Basic+*watchers]]\r\n[[related subtabs - universal]]\r\n[[list of rules]]\r\n[[not set or setting]]\r\n[[translatable cards]]\r\n[[default cards]]\r\n[[star cards]]\r\n[[not listed yet]]\r\n[[Settings defaults and help]]\r\n[[Advanced Search]]\r\n[[new+*self]]\r\n[[new+*self+*comment]]\r\n[[cquin]]'),(6493,'2013-05-24 22:28:12',80,149,'<p>{{Cards|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{{Types|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{{list of rules|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>'),(6494,'2013-05-24 22:28:25',80,149,'<p>{{Cards|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{{Types|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{{Rules|titled}}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>'),(6495,'2013-05-24 22:34:13',793,149,'<p>The secret to Wagn\'s magic is simple:</p>\r\n<blockquote><strong>It\'s all in the cards.</strong></blockquote>\r\n<p>Everything you\'ll ever do on Wagn will involve creating, reading, updating, and deleting cards.</p>'),(6496,'2013-05-24 22:34:52',793,149,'<p>The secret to Wagn\'s magic is simple:</p>\r\n<blockquote>{{Wagn\'s Secret|open}}</blockquote>\r\n<p>Everything you\'ll ever do on Wagn will involve creating, reading, updating, and deleting cards.</p>'),(6497,'2013-05-24 22:35:01',794,149,'<p>It\'s all in the cards.</p>'),(6501,'2013-05-24 22:36:46',793,149,'<p>Everything you\'ll ever do on Wagn will involve creating, reading, updating, and deleting cards.</p>\r\n<blockquote>{{Wagn\'s Secret|open}}</blockquote>\r\n<p></p>'),(6507,'2013-05-24 22:40:59',793,149,'<p>\"Cards\" are Wagn\'s building blocks. Everything you do on Wagn involves creating, reading, updating, and deleting cards. Here\'s a simple one:</p>\r\n<blockquote>{{Wagn\'s Secret|open}}</blockquote>\r\n<p></p>'),(6508,'2013-05-28 20:18:14',80,149,'<p></p>\r\n<p></p>'),(6509,'2013-07-18 21:38:43',404,149,'<p>(Learn more about [[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/internationalization|translating Wagn into other languages]].)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Here are all of the cards to translate into another language. Be sure not to edit the name of any cards that begin with a star (*), or their content unless you are explicitly asked to do so here:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Cardtypes<br></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Cardtype <strong>names</strong> themselves should be translated, as well as the <strong>description</strong> of each Cardtype:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Cardtype+*type+by name}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Edit help<br></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>All of the customizable edit help <strong>contents</strong>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*edit help+*right+by name}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Sidebar</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>names</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of these cards in the sidebar:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Menu|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Administrator Menu|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Config|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Account-related</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>description</strong> of each Role, and the two account cards:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Anyone|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Anyone signed in|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Administrator|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{Anonymous|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Wagn Bot|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> of \"cards with accounts\" and the <strong>content</strong> of \"*account\".</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Cards with accounts|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*account|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of these:</p>\n<blockquote>{{Invite Success|closed}}\n<p>{{Request Sent|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Signup Success|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> of these. Make sure you update the reference at the end of the first three to the corresponding new name of one of the three cards just above.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*invite|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*request|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*signup|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Role+*type+*default|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Related tab\'s subtabs</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> only of these:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*incoming+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*outgoing+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*plusses+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*community+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*account+*right+*content|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{watcher instructions for related tab+*right+*content|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Cardtype+watcher instructions for related tab+*type plus right+*content|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{watcher instructions for related tab|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Miscellaneous</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> of *title, which appears in most web browsers\' title bar:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*title|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> of the default home card &mdash; make sure to change both the name of the card itself, and update *home to the new name:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Home|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*home|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Similarly, change the <strong>name</strong> of \"Default Layout\" and the reference to it in \"*all+*layout\". Also, translate Home, Recent, and the credit text (\"Wheeled by...\" in the <strong>content</strong> of \"Default Layout\":</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Default Layout|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*all+*layout|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Just the <strong>names</strong> of these cards (used to order search results):</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{by name|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{by update|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{by create|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of this card:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Form submission thanks|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>names</strong> only of these cards:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{discussion|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{tag|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{description|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{email config|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> of this card (the cards named do not exist and don\'t need to):</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*input+*right+*option|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(6510,'2013-07-18 21:38:44',410,149,'<p>Since so many capabilities are built with Wagn itself, new  installations come with several hundred cards by default. Most of them  are listed here (not including many cards that make up some of the plus  cards below). The default cards themselves are actually maintained on  en.dwagn.org</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[Cardtypes]]</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Each includes a description card, and links here to relevant documentation.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Administrative<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Account Request]]</p>\n<p>[[Cardtype]]</p>\n<p>[[Role]]</p>\n<p>[[Set]]</p>\n<p>[[Setting]]</p>\n<p>[[User]] &mdash; and [[User+*type+*accountable]] makes it possible for them to have accounts.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Data types</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Basic]]<br>[[Phrase]]<br>[[PlainText]]<br>[[Image]] &mdash; and [[Image+*right+*default]] makes any new card ending in +Image to be of type Image.<br>[[File]]</p>\n<p>[[Pointer]]</p>\n<p>[[Search]]</p>\n<p>[[Toggle]]<br>[[Number]]<br>[[Date]]<br>[[HTML]] &mdash; and [[HTML+*type+*default]] sets new ones to be editable only by Administrators.</p>\n<p>[[Ruby]] &mdash; but they\'re turned off by default</p>\n<p>[[Script]] &mdash; but they\'re turned off by default</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Sidebar<br></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Menu]]<br>[[Administrator Menu]]<br>[[Config]] &mdash; in Administrator links</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Account-related</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Roles and Accounts<br></h2>\n<p>Each includes a description card, and links here to relevant documentation.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Anyone]]<br>[[Anyone signed in]]<br>[[Administrator]]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[Anonymous]]</p>\n<p>[[Wagn Bot]]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Other<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Cards with accounts]] &mdash; lists account-holding cards (typically [[Users]], included on [[*account]]<br>[[Invite Success]] &mdash; See [[/wagn/account#Administering%20accounts]] for more on this and the next two.<br>[[Request Sent]]<br>[[Signup Success]]</p>\n<p>[[Role+*type+*content]] &mdash; form for Role cards</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>For ordering searches</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>So that you can do things like [[User+*type+by create]] (people in the order they registered an account).</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[by name+*right+*content]]<br>[[by update+*right+*content]]]]<br>[[by create+*right+*content]]]]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Miscellaneous</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>[[Home]] &mdash; default front page</li>\n<li>[[email config+*right+*content]] &mdash; form for emails sent via [[flexible email]]. Help text is [[email config+*right+*edit help]].</li>\n<li>[[discussion+*right+*default]] &mdash; so that any [[plus card]] ending with +[[discussion]] allows comments<br>[[tags]] &mdash; for tagging, e.g. in the [[Related tab]]. [[tags+*right+*default]] makes any card +tags a Pointer</li>\n<li>[[Form submission thanks]] &mdash; see [[thank you messages]]</li>\n<li>[[description]] &mdash; for the built in descriptions of cardtypes and roles<br>[[Default Layout]] &mdash; the default layout, specified by [[*all+*layout]]. See [[custom layouts]].</li>\n<li>Regarding [[notifications]]:<br> {{watcher instructions for related tab|closed}}</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[Star cards]] (everything below)<br></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{star cards}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(6511,'2013-07-18 21:38:44',81,149,'<div>{{Menu|open}}</div>\r\n<div>{{Administrator Menu|open}}</div>\r\n<div>{{*credit|content}}</div>'),(6513,'2013-07-18 21:50:44',81,149,'<div>{{Menu|open}}</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>{{Wagneer Menu|open}}</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>{{Administrator Menu|open}}</div>\r\n<div>{{*credit|content}}</div>'),(6514,'2013-07-18 22:03:51',795,149,'<p>Key [[http://wagn.org/Features| Features]]</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/cards|cards]]</li>\r\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/types|types]]</li>\r\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/rules|rules]]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Key [[http://wagn.org/Syntax Reference| Syntax]]</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/link_syntax|links]]</li>\r\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/inclusion_syntax|inclusions]]</li>\r\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/WQL_syntax|queries]]</li>\r\n</ul>'),(6515,'2013-07-18 22:16:57',796,149,'{\"name\":\"_self\"}'),(6516,'2013-07-18 22:16:57',797,149,'[[Administrator]]'),(6517,'2013-07-18 22:26:36',73,149,'<h1>Basics</h1>\r\n<div>Set your site name, home card, and logo image:</div>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div>{{*title|closed;type:Phrase}}</div>\r\n<div>{{*home|closed;type:Phrase}}</div>\r\n<div>{{*logo|closed;type:Image}}</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h1>Rules</h1>\r\n<div>Cards are configured by creating <em>rules</em>. All the rules impacting a given card can be accessed from the card menu via the \"advanced\" item. Here are the site-wide defaults:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<blockquote>{{*all|open}}</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h1>Email / Account Configuration</h1>\r\n<div>Configure account-related emails here:</div>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div>{{*request|closed}}</div>\r\n<div>{{*signup|closed}}</div>\r\n{{*invite|closed}}</blockquote>\r\n<div>By default, system emails come from [[/Wagn_Bot?view=account| Wagn Bot\'s email address]].</div>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div>{{Wagn Bot|closed}}</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div>You can [[http://wagn.org/custom_sign-up_information|further configure signups]] by[[http://wagn.org/formatting|formatting]][[Account Request]] and [[User]] cards.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><em>[[http://wagn.org/account#Administering%20accounts | Learn more about